  speakerType: 1
  speakerName: "V\u0169"
  text: "B\xECnh t\u0129nh anh \u01A1i. \u0110\u01B0a em xem... Ui gi\u1EDDi, c\xE1i
    n\u1EAFp pin b\u1ECB l\u1ECFng, pin n\xF3 tu\u1ED9t ra ngo\xE0i r\u1ED3i th\xEC
    l\xEAn \u0111i\u1EC7n sao \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. Anh d\xF9ng Mic m\xE0 'b\u1EA1o
    l\u1EF1c' th\u1EBF!(V\u0169 th\xE1o n\u1EAFp, l\u1EAFp l\u1EA1i pin \u0111\xFAng
    c\u1EF1c, v\u1ED7 nh\u1EB9 v\xE0o \u0111\u1EA7u Mic: B\u1EE5p b\u1EE5p... Alo
    alo!)\r\n"
